-- ============================================================
-- AI Tool Content Update Script - Batch 1 (Tools 1-50)
-- English content_html, natural tone, SEO-safe
-- ============================================================

-- Rytr
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Rytr?</h2><p>Rytr is a budget-friendly AI writing assistant aimed at marketers, bloggers, and small business owners who need decent copy without the premium price tag. It covers over 40 use cases from product descriptions to social media captions, and while it does not match the depth of tools like Jasper or Copy.ai, the value-for-money ratio is hard to beat if you are working with a tight budget.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Over 40 content templates span blog ideas, email drafts, ad copy, and more. A built-in plagiarism checker helps ensure originality. You can write in 30+ languages and adjust the tone to match your brand. The Chrome extension brings Rytr into Gmail, WordPress, and social platforms without switching tabs.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free plan offers 10,000 characters per month. The Saver plan at $9/month bumps that up significantly, while the Unlimited plan at $29/month removes character limits entirely and adds priority support.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'rytr';

-- Sudowrite
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Sudowrite?</h2><p>Sudowrite was built from the ground up for fiction writers, and it shows. While most AI writing tools focus on marketing copy, Sudowrite understands narrative arcs, character voice, and sensory detail. Think of it as a writing partner that helps you push past creative blocks and develop richer prose, without trying to take over your story.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>The Story Engine generates detailed beats and full chapters from your outline. A Describe feature uses all five senses to flesh out scenes and characters. Write mode auto-completes your next paragraphs in your style, while Rewrite offers alternative phrasings. The Canvas provides a visual space for organizing plot structure.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Plans start at $19/month for the Hobby tier. Professional plans offer higher word limits for more prolific writers. A free trial is available so you can test the features before committing.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'sudowrite';

-- Wordtune
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Wordtune?</h2><p>Wordtune goes beyond basic grammar checking. Instead of just fixing errors, it understands what you are trying to say and offers entirely new ways to phrase it, making your writing clearer, more engaging, or more concise depending on what you need. It is especially popular among non-native English speakers and professionals who want their emails and documents to sound polished.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>The Rewrite engine suggests alternative versions of your sentences with different tones. Toggle between casual and formal registers instantly. Shorten or expand text to hit the right length. Spices add relevant stats, analogies, or cultural references to enrich your writing. A browser extension integrates with Google Docs, Gmail, Slack, and more.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free plan includes limited rewrites per day. Wordtune Premium starts at $9.99/month and unlocks unlimited rewrites, tone adjustments, and all the advanced features.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'wordtune';

-- Anyword
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Anyword?</h2><p>Anyword takes a data-driven approach to copywriting. Rather than just generating text, it predicts how well that text will perform with your target audience using a proprietary Predictive Performance Score. For marketing teams running paid ads, email campaigns, or landing pages, this scoring system takes a lot of the guesswork out of copy optimization.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Every piece of generated copy comes with a performance score that estimates engagement potential. Custom brand guidelines ensure the AI stays consistent with your voice and terminology. Multi-channel support covers ads, emails, landing pages, blog posts, and SMS. A/B testing insights help refine your copy over time based on actual results.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The Starter plan begins at $39/month with core features. Data-Driven plans with Predictive Performance Scores start at $79/month. Enterprise plans with custom integrations are available for larger teams.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'anyword';

-- Hypotenuse AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Hypotenuse AI?</h2><p>Hypotenuse AI is purpose-built for e-commerce. If you run an online store with hundreds or thousands of products, writing unique, SEO-friendly descriptions for each one is a nightmare. Hypotenuse automates that process, generating product copy, category pages, and even blog content that actually sounds like it was written for your brand.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Bulk product description generation handles catalogs of any size. The AI learns from your brand guidelines, past content, and product data to maintain consistency. SEO optimization is baked into the generation process. It also supports blog articles, social media posts, and ad copy alongside product content.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Plans start at $29/month for the Starter tier. Growth and Enterprise plans scale with content volume and add features like team collaboration and API access.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'hypotenuse-ai';

-- Simplified AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Simplified?</h2><p>Simplified bundles design, video editing, social media scheduling, and AI writing into one platform. Instead of paying for Canva plus a writing tool plus a scheduling tool, you get all of it in one place. It is aimed at small teams and solo creators who want a single workspace for their entire content pipeline.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>The AI Writer generates blog posts, ad copy, and social media captions in over 30 languages. A drag-and-drop graphic designer and video editor are built in. Social media scheduling and publishing let you plan content calendars. Brand kits keep your visual identity consistent across everything you create.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>There is a generous free plan with limited AI credits. Paid plans start at $12/month for individuals and scale up for teams with more seats and higher usage limits.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'simplified-ai';

-- Content at Scale
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Content at Scale?</h2><p>Content at Scale is built for one thing: producing long-form, SEO-optimized blog posts that can compete on Google. Give it a keyword, and it returns a 2,000-3,000+ word article with proper headings, internal linking suggestions, and an original structure. The output consistently scores high on AI detection tools, meaning it reads more like human writing than most competitors.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Full-length articles from a single keyword, complete with headers, FAQs, and meta descriptions. The platform includes a built-in AI content detector so you can check your own output. SEO scoring benchmarks your content against competitors. WordPress integration publishes directly to your blog.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Plans start at $250/month for 8 posts. Higher tiers offer more monthly posts and additional features. The pricing reflects the enterprise-grade long-form output rather than short snippets.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'content-at-scale';

-- LongShot AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is LongShot AI?</h2><p>LongShot AI focuses on factual, research-backed long-form content. It pulls from live web sources and verifies claims as it writes, making it a solid choice for bloggers and content teams who need accuracy alongside SEO performance. The fact-checking layer is what separates it from tools that just generate plausible-sounding text.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Real-time fact-checking cross-references generated claims against web sources. SEO workflow tools guide you from keyword research through outline creation to final copy. Custom templates cover blog posts, listicles, how-to guides, and more. Team collaboration features support multi-writer workflows.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free plan offers limited monthly credits. Pro plans start at $19/month with expanded word limits and full feature access. Team plans are available for collaborative content operations.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'longshot-ai';

-- Peppertype
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Peppertype?</h2><p>Peppertype (now part of Pepper Content) started as a quick-fire AI copywriting tool and has evolved into a broader content marketing platform. It is popular in the startup and SMB space for generating marketing copy fast, covering everything from Google Ads to blog intros to product descriptions.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Over 35 content types are available from a simple interface. The AI generates multiple variations per request so you can pick the best one. A content quality score helps evaluate output before publishing. Integration with the broader Pepper Content marketplace connects you with human editors for final polish.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>A limited free plan is available. The Personal plan starts at $35/month with generous word limits. Team and Enterprise plans add collaboration tools and higher usage caps.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'peppertype';

-- Koala Writer
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Koala Writer?</h2><p>KoalaWriter is an AI writing tool laser-focused on producing SEO-optimized blog content from a single keyword. It integrates real-time SERP analysis into the writing process, so the generated articles are structured to compete with whatever is currently ranking on page one of Google.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>One-click article generation from a target keyword. Real-time SERP analysis shapes the article structure and content coverage. GPT-4o powers the writing engine for higher quality output. Automatic table of contents, FAQ sections, and internal linking suggestions are included. Amazon affiliate content generation is available for product review sites.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The Essentials plan starts at $9/month. Professional at $25/month adds GPT-4o access, more monthly articles, and advanced SEO features.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'koala-writer';

-- NeuralText
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is NeuralText?</h2><p>NeuralText combines keyword research, content briefs, and AI writing into a unified SEO workflow. Instead of bouncing between a keyword tool, a brief generator, and a writing assistant, you handle the entire content pipeline in one place. It is well-suited for SEO specialists and content teams who want a streamlined process from topic research to published article.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Keyword clustering groups related terms into content opportunities. Automated content briefs pull from top-ranking pages. The AI writer generates drafts aligned with your brief and target keywords. SERP analysis shows what the competition covers so you do not miss important subtopics.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Free trials are available. Paid plans start at $19/month for the Starter tier and go up to $119/month for the Business plan with unlimited documents and advanced features.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'neuraltext';

-- Frase
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Frase?</h2><p>Frase is an AI-powered SEO content platform that helps you research, write, and optimize articles in one workflow. It automatically analyzes what top-ranking competitors cover for any given keyword and generates a comprehensive content brief, so you know exactly what topics, questions, and headers to address before you start writing.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Automated SERP research and content brief generation save hours of manual analysis. The AI writer drafts articles based on your brief. A real-time content optimization score tracks how thoroughly you cover the topic compared to competitors. Question research surfaces the specific queries your audience is searching for.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Solo plans start at $14.99/month for individual creators. Basic at $44.99/month and Team at $114.99/month add more documents, collaboration tools, and advanced analytics.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'frase-io';

-- Scalenut
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Scalenut?</h2><p>Scalenut positions itself as an all-in-one SEO and content marketing platform. From keyword research and topic clustering through outline generation and AI writing, it covers the full content lifecycle. The Cruise Mode feature is particularly notable, producing full-length SEO articles with minimal manual intervention.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Cruise Mode automates end-to-end article creation from keyword to draft. Topic clustering identifies content gaps and opportunities across your niche. The AI writer handles blog posts, product descriptions, and marketing copy. Real-time SEO scoring benchmarks your content against top SERP results.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The Essential plan starts at $39/month. Growth at $79/month adds more articles and advanced features. Pro at $149/month is designed for agencies and larger teams.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'scalenut';

-- QuillBot
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is QuillBot?</h2><p>QuillBot is one of the most popular paraphrasing tools on the internet, used heavily by students, academics, and content writers. Paste in any text and it rewrites it while preserving the original meaning, offering multiple modes from standard to creative to academic. It has expanded into a full writing suite with grammar checking, summarization, and citation tools.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>The paraphraser offers seven rewriting modes including Standard, Fluency, Formal, Creative, and Academic. A grammar checker catches errors and suggests improvements. The summarizer condenses long texts into key points. A citation generator creates properly formatted references in APA, MLA, and Chicago styles. Extensions for Chrome, Word, and Google Docs integrate into your workflow.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Basic paraphrasing is free with some feature restrictions. QuillBot Premium at $9.95/month unlocks all modes, unlimited paraphrasing length, advanced grammar checks, and plagiarism detection.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'quillbot';

-- Grammarly
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Grammarly?</h2><p>Grammarly has become synonymous with writing assistance. Used by over 30 million people daily, it catches grammar mistakes, suggests clearer phrasing, detects tone, and now includes generative AI features for drafting and rewriting. It works virtually everywhere you type, from email clients to social media to word processors.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Real-time grammar, spelling, and punctuation corrections are the foundation. Beyond that, style and clarity suggestions help refine your writing. Tone detection lets you know how your message will come across. GrammarlyGO uses generative AI to draft replies, rewrite paragraphs, and brainstorm ideas. Integrations span the Chrome browser, Microsoft Office, Google Docs, Slack, and even your phone keyboard.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free plan covers basic grammar and spelling checks. Grammarly Premium at $12/month adds advanced style suggestions, tone detection, and plagiarism checking. Business plans start at $15/member/month for team features.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'grammarly';

-- Hemingway Editor
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Hemingway Editor?</h2><p>Named after Ernest Hemingway, this editor does exactly what the name implies: it pushes you toward bold, clear writing. Paste in your text and it highlights overly complex sentences, passive voice, excessive adverbs, and hard-to-read passages using a simple color-coding system. It will not write for you, but it will make your existing writing significantly tighter.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Color-coded highlights identify different readability issues at a glance. A readability grade score tells you the education level needed to understand your text. Passive voice detection encourages more direct, active writing. The latest version adds AI editing suggestions. Available as both a free web app and a paid desktop application.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The web version is free to use. The desktop app is a one-time purchase of $19.99 with no subscription required. A new Hemingway Editor Plus subscription adds AI assistance features.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'hemingway-editor';

-- Notion AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Notion AI?</h2><p>Notion AI adds artificial intelligence directly into Notion, the popular all-in-one workspace. Rather than switching to a separate AI tool, you can summon AI assistance right where you are already writing notes, managing projects, and building wikis. It handles drafting, summarizing, translating, brainstorming, and extracting action items from your existing Notion documents.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Draft new content, expand on bullet points, or rewrite existing text without leaving your workspace. Summarize long meeting notes or documents into key takeaways. Translate content across languages. Extract action items and next steps from meeting agendas. Q&A search across your entire Notion workspace surfaces relevant information from your own knowledge base.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Notion AI is an add-on at $10/member/month on top of your existing Notion plan. Notion itself offers free, Plus ($10/month), and Business ($18/month) tiers.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'notion-ai';

-- Lex AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Lex?</h2><p>Lex is a minimalist AI-powered writing editor that feels like a cleaned-up Google Doc with GPT built in. Hit a keyboard shortcut and the AI continues writing from where you left off, matching your tone and style. It is designed for focused, long-form writing without the clutter of toolbars, menus, and feature overload.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>A distraction-free editor prioritizes clean, focused writing. AI auto-complete continues your train of thought naturally. Title suggestions, feedback requests, and collaborative commenting are built in. Version history tracks your changes over time. The interface stays intentionally simple.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Lex offers a free plan with limited AI usage. The Premium plan at $8/month removes limits and adds advanced AI features for more serious writers.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'lex-ai';

-- AI21 Wordspice
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is AI21 Wordspice?</h2><p>AI21 Wordspice is a sentence-level enhancement tool from AI21 Labs. It takes your plain sentences and suggests more vivid, expressive alternatives, essentially adding flavor to flat writing. Unlike full-document generators, it works at the micro level, helping you improve individual sentences one at a time.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Sentence-level rewriting suggests more engaging and vivid alternatives. Multiple options let you pick the version that fits your voice. Contextual understanding preserves your original meaning while improving impact. It is lightweight and simple to use without any learning curve.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Wordspice is free to use as a standalone web tool. AI21 Labs also offers API access for their broader suite of language models for developers building custom applications.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'ai21-wordspice';

-- Text Blaze
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Text Blaze?</h2><p>Text Blaze is a text expansion and template automation tool that saves you from typing the same things over and over. Create snippets with dynamic variables, form fields, and logic, then trigger them anywhere with a short abbreviation. Customer support teams, salespeople, and anyone who sends repetitive messages love it for the hours it saves each week.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Custom snippets with dynamic fields (names, dates, placeholders) fill in automatically. Nested snippets and conditional logic handle complex templates. Team sharing lets everyone use the same approved templates. Works across any website or web app through a Chrome extension. Integration with Google Sheets pulls data directly into your snippets.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free plan supports basic snippets. Pro at $2.99/month adds forms and dynamic logic. Business at $6.99/month includes team features, admin controls, and priority support.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'text-blaze';

-- AdCreative AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is AdCreative.ai?</h2><p>AdCreative.ai generates high-converting ad creatives using AI trained on millions of successful ad campaigns. Upload your brand assets, describe your product, and it produces dozens of ad variations optimized for platforms like Facebook, Instagram, and Google Ads. The creative scoring system predicts which designs will perform best before you spend a cent on media.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>AI-generated ad banners and social media creatives in various sizes and formats. Each creative gets a conversion score predicting its performance. Brand kit integration keeps colors, fonts, and logos consistent. Competitor ad analysis shows what others in your space are running. Direct integration with Meta and Google ad platforms speeds up campaign launches.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The Starter plan begins at $29/month with 10 downloads. Premium plans scale up with more downloads, team seats, and advanced analytics. A 7-day free trial is available.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'adcreative-ai';

-- Writesonic
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Writesonic?</h2><p>Writesonic is an AI content platform that covers a wide range of writing tasks, from short ad copy to full-length blog articles. Its Chatsonic feature adds a ChatGPT-like conversational interface with real-time web access, while the article writer handles long-form SEO content. It has become a popular alternative for teams that want ChatGPT-level capabilities in a more structured content creation environment.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Chatsonic provides conversational AI with current web data and image generation. The Article Writer generates SEO-optimized blog posts up to 3,000 words. Over 100 templates cover ads, emails, product descriptions, and more. Botsonic lets you build custom AI chatbots trained on your website data. Brand Voice learning keeps content consistent with your style.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>A free plan offers limited credits. Individual plans start at $16/month. Teams and Business plans scale with more words, seats, and advanced features.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'writesonic';

-- Copy.ai
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Copy.ai?</h2><p>Copy.ai started as a simple copywriting tool and has grown into a full-scale GTM (go-to-market) AI platform. It helps sales and marketing teams automate content workflows end to end, from generating blog posts and social media copy to enriching CRM data and personalizing outreach at scale. The workflow automation engine is what sets it apart from simpler writing tools.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>AI-powered workflows automate multi-step content processes. Over 90 copywriting templates cover every marketing channel. The Infobase feature stores your brand info so the AI references accurate details. CRM integrations with Salesforce and HubSpot enrich and personalize sales outreach. Chat interface handles ad-hoc content generation requests.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>A generous free plan includes 2,000 words per month. Pro at $36/month provides unlimited words. Team and Enterprise plans add workflow automation, integrations, and admin controls.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'copy-ai';

-- Jasper
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Jasper?</h2><p>Jasper is one of the original and most well-known AI writing platforms for marketing teams. It has evolved from a simple blog writer into an enterprise-grade content platform with brand voice learning, campaign management, and team collaboration. Fortune 500 companies use it to scale content production while maintaining brand consistency across channels.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Brand Voice and Brand Knowledge features train the AI on your specific tone, style, and company information. Campaign tools manage multi-channel content for product launches. Over 50 templates cover blog posts, ads, emails, and social media. Jasper Chat provides a conversational AI interface for brainstorming and quick drafts. Built-in image generation through Jasper Art rounds out the creative suite.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Creator starts at $39/month for individual marketers. Pro at $59/month adds Brand Voice and collaboration. Business pricing is custom and includes advanced security and admin features.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'jasper';

-- Surfer SEO
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Surfer SEO?</h2><p>Surfer SEO is a data-driven content optimization platform that analyzes what makes top-ranking pages successful and helps you reverse-engineer their approach. It scans the current SERP for your target keyword, identifies content gaps, and gives you a real-time score as you write. Many SEO professionals consider it the gold standard for on-page optimization.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>The Content Editor provides a real-time optimization score that tracks keyword usage, content structure, word count, and topical coverage. SERP Analyzer breaks down the top-ranking pages for any keyword. Content Audit reviews existing articles and suggests improvements. Surfer AI can generate full, optimized articles from a keyword. Integrations with Google Docs, WordPress, and Jasper fit into existing workflows.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Essential starts at $89/month for up to 30 articles. Scale at $129/month adds more articles and Surfer AI credits. Enterprise plans are available for agencies and large teams.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'surfer-seo';

-- GrowthBar
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is GrowthBar?</h2><p>GrowthBar is an SEO tool with a strong AI writing component, designed for bloggers and content marketers who want keyword research, competitive analysis, and AI-powered content generation in a single platform. Its Chrome extension is particularly handy, giving you SEO insights right on the Google search results page.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>AI content generation produces blog outlines and full drafts optimized for your target keywords. Keyword research includes difficulty scores, search volume, and related terms. Competitor analysis reveals backlink profiles and top-performing content. The Chrome extension surfaces SEO data as you browse search results. Content optimization scoring helps you hit the right benchmarks.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The Standard plan starts at $36/month. Pro at $74.25/month and Agency at $149.25/month add more keyword lookups, AI-generated articles, and team seats.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'growthbar';

-- Outranking
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Outranking?</h2><p>Outranking is an AI-powered SEO content strategy platform that manages the entire lifecycle of your content, from first-draft creation through ongoing optimization and performance tracking. It focuses on building topical authority by helping you plan content clusters and interlinked articles around core topics.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Automated content briefs with SERP analysis set the foundation. The AI writer creates first drafts aligned with your SEO strategy. Internal linking recommendations strengthen your site structure. Content decay monitoring alerts you when older articles need updating. Authority-building workflows help you plan topic clusters strategically.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The Starter plan begins at $29/month. SEO Writer at $79/month and SEO Strategist at $149/month add more documents, advanced analytics, and automation features.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'outranking';

-- Article Forge
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Article Forge?</h2><p>Article Forge is a fully automated article generator. Give it a keyword and it produces a complete, unique article in about 60 seconds. It uses deep learning rather than templates, and while the output varies in quality, the speed and hands-off approach appeal to website owners who need volume at scale.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>One-click article generation from just a keyword. Automatic section headings, images, and video embedding. Built-in scheduling can auto-publish to WordPress on a set cadence. Bulk article generation handles large content requirements. The tool also integrates with WordAi for additional rewriting options.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>A single plan is available at $27/month (billed annually) for up to 250,000 words per month. A 5-day free trial lets you test the output quality before subscribing.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'article-forge';

-- Kafkai
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Kafkai?</h2><p>Kafkai is an AI article writer designed specifically for SEO-focused content generation. It uses niche-trained models rather than general-purpose language models, meaning you pick your industry vertical and the AI writes with domain-specific knowledge. This approach tends to produce more relevant and accurate content for specialized topics.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Niche-trained AI models cover specific industries like health, tech, finance, and marketing. Three generation modes handle different content needs: quick drafts, detailed articles, and keyword-driven pieces. Seed article mode generates variations based on existing content. Bulk generation supports high-volume content operations.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The Writer plan starts at $29/month for 100 articles. Professional at $49/month and Business at $129/month increase the monthly article limit and add advanced features.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'kafkai';

-- ClosersCopy
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is ClosersCopy?</h2><p>ClosersCopy is a copywriting AI that leans heavily into sales and persuasion frameworks. It ships with built-in marketing frameworks like PAS (Problem-Agitate-Solution), AIDA, and BAB (Before-After-Bridge), making it a favorite among direct response copywriters and sales teams who care about conversion-oriented writing.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Built-in sales and marketing copywriting frameworks guide persuasive writing. A drag-and-drop workflow builder creates custom content pipelines. Over 700 proprietary marketing templates cover everything from sales letters to email sequences. The Community Library lets users share and discover custom frameworks. No word limit means you can generate freely once subscribed.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Power at $49.99/month, Superpower at $79.99/month, and Superpower Squad at $99.99/month, each adding more machine access and seats. Lifetime deals are occasionally available.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'closerscopy';

-- Wordhero
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Wordhero?</h2><p>Wordhero is a straightforward AI writing assistant that covers the basics well without overwhelming you with features. It offers over 70 writing tools for blog posts, ad copy, product descriptions, and more. The appeal is simplicity and an affordable flat-rate pricing model that does not charge per word.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Over 70 AI writing tools handle a wide range of content types. A long-form editor supports blog posts and articles. The interface is clean and beginner-friendly. Built-in keyword assistance helps improve SEO. No per-word billing means predictable costs regardless of output volume.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The monthly plan is $49/month with unlimited content generation. A popular lifetime deal is sometimes available for a one-time payment, which offers exceptional long-term value.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'wordhero';

-- Writer.com
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Writer?</h2><p>Writer (writer.com) is an enterprise AI writing platform built for large organizations that need consistent, on-brand content at scale. It goes far beyond grammar checking by enforcing custom style guides, terminology rules, and brand voice across every piece of content your team produces. Think of it as Grammarly for enterprises with serious compliance and governance needs.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Custom style guide enforcement applies your company''s specific rules across all content. Brand Voice analysis ensures consistency regardless of who is writing. Terminology management maintains approved language and catches non-compliant terms. Recaps summarize long documents and meetings. Palmyra, Writer''s own LLM, powers the platform without sending data to third parties. Full enterprise security and compliance features are included.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Team plans start at $18/user/month. Enterprise pricing is custom and includes dedicated support, advanced security controls, and custom integrations.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'writer-com';

-- Copysmith
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Copysmith?</h2><p>Copysmith is an AI copywriting tool designed primarily for e-commerce and enterprise teams. Its strength lies in generating product descriptions, catalog content, and marketing copy at scale, with workflow features like bulk generation and API access that larger operations need. It integrates with major e-commerce platforms to streamline product content creation.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Bulk content generation handles product catalogs with hundreds or thousands of SKUs. Templates span product descriptions, ad copy, blog posts, and landing pages. Campaign builder organizes content by marketing initiative. API access enables integration with custom workflows and e-commerce platforms like Shopify. Team collaboration tools support review and approval processes.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Starter begins at $19/month. Professional at $59/month adds bulk generation and integrations. Enterprise plans include custom solutions for high-volume content needs.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'copysmith';

-- ContentBot
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is ContentBot?</h2><p>ContentBot is an AI content generator that covers both short and long-form writing. It has carved out a niche with its automated blog content feature and an interesting addition called Paraphraser, which rewrites existing content while maintaining the original message. The platform also includes workflow automation for content teams.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>The AI blog writer generates complete articles from topics or outlines. A paraphrasing tool rewrites content while preserving intent. Over 45 short-form content tools handle ads, emails, and social posts. An Autopilot feature can generate and schedule content automatically. WordPress integration simplifies the publishing workflow.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>A free plan includes limited monthly words. Prepaid credits start at $1 per 1,000 words. The Premium plan at $29.50/month provides 50,000 words and full feature access.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'contentbot';

-- Nichesss
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Nichesss?</h2><p>Nichesss is an AI writing tool focused on helping entrepreneurs and marketers generate niche business ideas, marketing copy, and content. What makes it different is the business ideation angle: it does not just write content, it helps you brainstorm viable business concepts for specific niches and then generates the marketing materials to go with them.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Business idea generation for specific niches combines market thinking with content creation. Marketing copy templates cover ads, emails, and social posts. Blog post generation handles long and short-form content. The interface is minimal and gets straight to the point without unnecessary complexity.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Pricing starts at $19/month for the Rookie plan. Higher tiers increase monthly output limits. A free trial is available to test the idea generation and writing features.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'nichesss';

-- Smart Copy (Unbounce)
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Smart Copy?</h2><p>Smart Copy is the AI copywriting tool from Unbounce, the popular landing page platform. It was originally called Snazzy AI before Unbounce acquired it. The focus is on generating conversion-optimized marketing copy, especially for landing pages, ads, and email campaigns. The Unbounce integration means your generated copy flows seamlessly into your landing pages.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Over 45 templates optimized for marketing and conversion content. Remix mode creates variations of existing copy for testing. Expand mode takes short bullet points and turns them into polished paragraphs. The Chrome extension lets you generate copy on any website. Direct integration with Unbounce landing pages streamlines the design-to-launch workflow.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>A free plan allows limited daily generations. The Essential plan at $9/month removes limits. Unbounce subscribers get Smart Copy included with their existing plan.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'smart-copy';

-- GoCharlie
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is GoCharlie?</h2><p>GoCharlie is a multimodal AI content platform that handles text, images, and even audio content. Named after a friendly AI character, it positions itself as an all-in-one creative assistant for solopreneurs and small marketing teams who want one tool to generate blog posts, social media graphics, ad copy, and more.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Multi-format content generation covers text, images, and audio in one platform. Charlie Blog creates long-form blog posts with SEO considerations. Social media content generation includes both copy and visuals. Built-in image generation eliminates the need for a separate image tool. A conversational AI chat interface handles ad-hoc requests.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>A free plan provides limited monthly credits. The Founder plan at $39/month offers generous usage across all content types. Higher tiers add team features and increased generation limits.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'gocharlie';

-- ParagraphAI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is ParagraphAI?</h2><p>ParagraphAI is designed to help anyone write better and faster, regardless of skill level. It works especially well for people who struggle with written communication, including non-native speakers and professionals who need quick, polished messages. The mobile app makes it easy to compose texts, emails, and messages on the go.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Smart reply suggestions help you respond quickly to emails and messages. A grammar and spelling checker works in real time. Tone adjustment lets you shift between professional, friendly, and casual registers. The mobile app is polished and designed for on-the-go writing. Translation support helps multilingual communication.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free plan covers basic features with usage limits. ParagraphAI Pro at $9.99/month unlocks unlimited writing, all templates, and advanced AI features.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'paragraphai';

-- Writecream
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Writecream?</h2><p>Writecream is an AI-powered outreach and content platform that stands out with its personalized cold outreach features. Beyond standard blog and ad copy generation, it creates personalized icebreakers for cold emails and LinkedIn messages by analyzing your prospect''s profile or website, making it popular with sales teams and recruiters.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Personalized icebreaker generation for cold emails and LinkedIn messages. AI-generated voicemails and audio content. Blog writing, ad copy, and social media content tools. SEO article generation with keyword optimization. Image icebreakers create personalized visual outreach assets.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>A free plan offers limited credits. The Starter plan at $49/month provides generous credits across all features. Unlimited plans are available for heavy users.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'writecream';

-- Hoppy Copy
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Hoppy Copy?</h2><p>Hoppy Copy is an AI copywriting tool built exclusively for email marketing. While most AI writers try to do everything, Hoppy Copy focuses on one thing: helping you write email campaigns that get opened, read, and clicked. It covers newsletters, drip sequences, welcome emails, and promotional blasts with templates designed specifically for inbox engagement.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Email-specific AI templates cover newsletters, sequences, promotional campaigns, and transactional emails. Spam check analyzes your email for deliverability red flags. Competitor email monitoring tracks what other companies in your space are sending. A/B subject line testing generates multiple variations. Integration with major email platforms simplifies implementation.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The Starter plan begins at $29/month with 20,000 words. The Pro plan at $49/month increases word limits and adds advanced features like competitor monitoring.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'hoppy-copy';

-- CopyMonkey
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is CopyMonkey?</h2><p>CopyMonkey is laser-focused on Amazon listing optimization. It uses AI to generate and optimize product titles, bullet points, descriptions, and backend keywords specifically for the Amazon marketplace. For Amazon sellers, this is a specialist tool that understands A9 algorithm requirements in a way generic writing tools simply do not.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Amazon listing generation and optimization tuned for the A9 algorithm. Keyword integration maximizes search visibility within the marketplace. Competitor analysis reveals what top sellers are doing differently. Bullet point and description optimization improves both search ranking and conversion. A/B testing insights help you refine your listings over time.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Plans start at $49/month for single sellers. Higher tiers support multiple listings and brands. Agency plans are available for Amazon consultants managing multiple clients.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'copymonkey';

-- Regie.ai
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Regie.ai?</h2><p>Regie.ai is a generative AI platform built for sales teams. It automates the creation of personalized outreach sequences, sales emails, and prospecting content. The AI researches your prospects and crafts messages tailored to their role, company, and pain points, making cold outreach feel more like a warm introduction.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Auto-pilot mode researches prospects and generates personalized outreach sequences automatically. Content management organizes approved messaging, case studies, and sales collateral. Persona-based content adapts messaging to different buyer roles. CRM integration with Salesforce and Outreach keeps everything in sync. Analytics track which messages and sequences perform best.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Pricing is based on the number of users and features needed. Plans start with a free tier for individual reps and scale to team and enterprise plans with advanced automation and integration capabilities.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'regie-ai';

-- Lavender
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Lavender?</h2><p>Lavender is an AI email assistant designed to help salespeople write emails that actually get replies. It analyzes your draft in real time and gives you a score out of 100, along with specific suggestions for improving subject lines, opening hooks, length, reading level, and mobile formatting. Sales teams report significant increases in reply rates after adopting it.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>A real-time email scoring system rates your draft and explains what to improve. Personalization assistant pulls insights about your recipient for more relevant outreach. GIF and meme integration adds personality to follow-ups. Mobile optimization ensures emails look good on phones. Team analytics reveal coaching opportunities across your sales org.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>A free plan provides limited email analysis. The Starter plan at $29/month unlocks unlimited scoring and basic features. Teams plans add coaching dashboards and analytics for managers.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'lavender';

-- SmartWriter
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is SmartWriter?</h2><p>SmartWriter automates personalized outreach by researching prospects across the web and generating custom messages based on what it finds. It scans LinkedIn profiles, company websites, news articles, and blog posts, then crafts contextually relevant emails, LinkedIn messages, and backlink outreach that reference specific, real details about the recipient.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Automated prospect research scans multiple data sources. Personalized email and LinkedIn message generation references real prospect details. Backlink outreach mode crafts messages for SEO link-building campaigns. Google review response generation helps local businesses manage reviews. Batch processing handles high-volume outreach campaigns.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The Basic plan starts at $59/month for up to 15 personalized emails per lead. Popular at $149/month and Pro at $359/month increase the number of leads, data sources, and generation volume.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'smartwriter';

-- Warmer.ai
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Warmer.ai?</h2><p>Warmer.ai generates personalized cold email openers by analyzing your prospect''s LinkedIn profile or website. The goal is simple: make the first line of your cold email feel personal and relevant, which is the hardest part to automate well. It is a focused, single-purpose tool that does one thing and does it efficiently.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Personalized email opening lines generated from prospect data. LinkedIn and website analysis for context-aware personalization. Multiple objective options let you tailor the tone for sales, networking, or partnerships. Batch generation processes multiple prospects at once. CSV import and export support integration with your existing outreach workflow.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Credit-based pricing starts at $59/month for a set number of prospect analyses. Higher tiers increase the monthly credit allotment for teams with larger outreach volumes.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'warmer-ai';

-- Easy-Peasy AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Easy-Peasy AI?</h2><p>Easy-Peasy AI is a friendly, approachable content generation platform that combines an AI writer, image generator, audio transcription, and chatbot in one tool. The name reflects its philosophy: making AI accessible to people who are not tech-savvy. It is a good entry point for small businesses and individual creators trying AI tools for the first time.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Over 80 content templates cover blog posts, ads, social media, and business documents. Built-in AI image generation from text prompts. Audio transcription converts recordings into text. Marky, the AI chatbot, handles conversational tasks and brainstorming. A clean, beginner-friendly interface with minimal learning curve.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free plan includes limited monthly generations across all features. The Basic plan starts at $5.99/month. Advanced plans scale up with more word credits, image generations, and transcription minutes.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'easy-peasy-ai';

-- Creaitor AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Creaitor AI?</h2><p>Creaitor AI is a multilingual content creation platform with a strong focus on SEO. It supports writing in over 45 languages natively, making it popular with international marketing teams and agencies serving clients across different language markets. The SERP analysis and optimization features work across all supported languages.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Content generation in 45+ languages with SEO optimization for each. SERP Beater tool analyzes competitor content and suggests how to outrank them. The AI chatbot assists with brainstorming and quick content tasks. Content scoring evaluates readability and SEO strength. Team collaboration tools support agency workflows.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The Starter plan begins at $9/month. Professional at $39/month adds SERP analysis and advanced tools. Agency plans at $99/month include multi-client management features.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'creaitor-ai';

-- Typli AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Typli?</h2><p>Typli is an AI writing and SEO tool that bundles article generation, keyword research, and even an AI image generator into a single affordable package. It targets bloggers and small businesses who want a do-it-all tool without paying for multiple separate subscriptions.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Long-form blog article generation with built-in SEO guidance. Keyword research tool identifies ranking opportunities. An AI image generator creates visuals alongside your content. Over 40 short-form content templates for quick copy tasks. The content rewriter paraphrases existing text while preserving meaning.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>A generous free plan includes daily usage limits. The Unlimited plan at $29/month removes all word and generation limits for unrestricted use.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'typli-ai';

-- Wordplay
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Wordplay?</h2><p>Wordplay is a long-form AI content writer that excels at producing full-length blog posts quickly. Its standout feature is factual article generation, where it pulls from verified sources to produce more accurate content. Unlike tools that only generate 500-word blurbs, Wordplay routinely produces 2,000-3,000+ word articles in a single generation.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Long-form articles up to 3,000+ words generated from a single prompt. Factual content mode uses verified sources for accuracy. Bulk article generation handles content calendars efficiently. SEO optimization is built into the generation workflow. Outline customization lets you structure articles before generation begins.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The Starter plan begins at $49/month for a limited number of articles. Professional and Agency plans increase the monthly article allowance and add priority processing.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'wordplay';

-- Moonbeam
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Moonbeam?</h2><p>Moonbeam is an AI writing assistant designed specifically for long-form content like essays, blog posts, and newsletters. Rather than generating generic text, it emphasizes structure and logical flow, helping you build well-organized, coherent pieces. The guided writing approach makes it feel more like working with an editor than talking to a text generator.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Luna, the AI assistant, helps brainstorm, outline, and draft long-form pieces. Custom writing clusters organize related topics and maintain consistency. Smart chat helps with research and ideation during the writing process. Templates for essays, blogs, newsletters, and social media posts provide starting points. The distraction-free editor keeps you focused on writing.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free plan offers limited monthly generations. Pro at $49/month unlocks unlimited generations, all templates, and priority processing.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'moonbeam';
